        Clause 6 [<span class="italic">Resource accounts: scrutiny</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0613P0-04563'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0613P0_20000612_GCR_99' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
