            <q>Page 4, line 14. at end insert&#x2014;</q>
            <q>("(3A) The Comptroller and Auditor General may examine any performance statement which he receives from a department under section 5 and report thereon.").</q>
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_32gc' title='Col. 32GC &mdash; HL Deb 12 June 2000 vol 613 c32GC' name='column_32gc' href='#column_32gc' rel='bookmark'>32GC</a>
