        Clause 16 [<span class="italic">Expenditure</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0613P0-04632'>
        <a name='S5LV0613P0_20000612_GCR_168'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-robin-bridgeman' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0613P0_20000612_GCR_168' title='Link to this speech by Mr Robin Bridgeman' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-robin-bridgeman" title="Mr Robin Bridgeman">Viscount Bridgeman</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            moved Amendment No. 26:
            <q>Page 9. line 31, after ("on") insert ("upstream").</q>
